item.title: 我的2022美赛心得
item.description: Write before beginning Before writing this paragraph, we just received the received notice on the official website, announcing that the four-day and 50 hour competition has officially come to an end. Looking back on the diaries I wrote these days, I have a lot of feelings. It is The first day to save the world, heaven and earth; The next day Newton attached himself to the body and created the formula; On the third day, he turned into Chen Jingrun and worked out a basket of draft paper; On the fourth day, he became Cao Xueqin, full of absurd words and bitter tears.

item.title: Chapter I: The Grand Hall
item.description: Three hundred and forty-eight years, six months, and nineteen days ago to-day, the Parisians awoke to the sound of all the bells in the triple circuit of the city, the university, and the town ringing a full peal. The sixth of January, 1482, is not, however, a day of which history has preserved the memory. There was nothing notable in the event which thus set the bells and the bourgeois of Paris in a ferment from early morning.
